comments: Yes. A great way to satisfy a writing credit.
Take it! It will make you want to make your own babies.
Great course! Anyone interested in children and education will find this class very interesting! Class was very straightforward and assignments were very clear.

This class is EXCELLENT. Fabulous experience for anyone who sees kids being part of their future...whether they are a future pediatrician, teacher or just a parent. You will never see children or education the same way again.One of the best classes offered at Yale.*note: this class does involve a lot of travel time. Make sure you have a little wiggle room in your schedule.
